{"tid":344060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"景林邨呎價15,359元 全港最貴公屋王(死支那狗183cm#35420入黎推post)","createTime":"2017-08-02T03:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T08:59:33.000Z","uid":65328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b879d6c09df1d0f72388f8f0416225b1860e0cc","tid":344060,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:49:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170802&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=57031322\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170802%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D57031322&d=9BvQd%2Fl7g%2B68%2F82dVwp3Cr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=53fb6eb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170802%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D57031322&h=06d709dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170802&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=57031322</a><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳公屋景林邨景桃樓高層28室，屬開放式劏房型一人公屋，不設任何間隔，沒有睡房，客廳僅設一個頗窄細窗，但有獨立廚房和廁所。差餉物業估價署資料顯示，全屋實用面積僅14.2平方米，即是153方呎。市場消息指，單位剛以天價易手，自由市場成交價高達235萬元，除開每呎15,359元，媲美港島私人屋苑造價。鰂魚涌太古城最舊一期翠湖台近期成交呎價介乎14,481元至17,667元。將軍澳樓王天晉近期二手呎價，個別呎價約1.6萬元，景林邨直逼「天晉價」﹔亦打破藍田公屋德田邨今年5月份所創下的每呎15,030元紀錄，成全港史上呎價最貴公屋王，亦誕下新界歷來首間呎價萬五公屋王。"},{"pid":"3c012c8a2703a9919881248565a936e4d9166cfd","tid":344060,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:54:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17daf29a7a05a51ff0c33d7b921e9e59cd8c2539","tid":344060,"uid":7934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:54:47.000Z","msg":"景林好撚舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32853c7c6a30e544998ace8cd610a16ccec0e15a","tid":344060,"uid":65328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:55:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>萬五蚊呎買得153呎嘅將軍澳公屋...<br />\n仲要唔近地鐵站...<br />\n黐撚咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上車盤"},{"pid":"876b8feb38f382efbb8f3904a162a8f